Ceremony Style

The Lover's Kiss
Presided over by a choir moogle, this ceremony is conducted in a light-hearted fashion and is sealed with a kiss.

The Spinner's Hand
Presided over by a female Officiant of the Graces, this traditional ceremony dedicated to the Twelve concludes with a symbolic toast to mark the start of your lives together.

The Solemn Oath
Presided over by a male Officiant of the Vows, this undenominational ceremony closes with the signing of an official pact before the assembled guests.

Procession

<If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),2))>You and your partner will enter the Ivory Chapel on foot<Else/>You and your partner may choose to enter the Ivory Chapel on foot, or seated upon <If(GreaterThan(IntegerParameter(1),2))>one of three enchanted gondolas<Else/>an enchanted gondola</If></If>.

Recession

<If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),2))>You and your partner will leave the Ivory Chapel on foot<Else/>You and your partner may choose to leave the Ivory Chapel on foot, or astride a chocobo</If>.

Bouquet

You may decide who will carry the bouquet during the ceremony. The bearer of the flowers will enter the chapel on the left.

Music

<If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),2))>Music to be played before the procession and during the reception will be selected for you<Else/>You may choose the music to be played before the procession and during the reception. <Link><If(IntegerParameter(2))><If(LessThanOrEqualTo(IntegerParameter(2),10))><switch(IntegerParameter(2),one,two,three,four,five,six,seven,eight,nine,ten)><Else/><Value>IntegerParameter(2)</Value></If><Else/><Value>IntegerParameter(2)</Value></If></Link> unique songs are available</If>.
